  <entry>
    <title>博客常用命令</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/09/19/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/09/19/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</id>
    <published>2022-09-19T15:01:29.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-09-19T15:08:18.829Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>记录下博客常用命令</p><p>新建文章：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new  postname</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>部署到github.io:  </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean                            <span class="comment">#清除缓存       可缩写hexo c</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo generate                         <span class="comment">#生成静态文件    可缩写hexo g</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy                           <span class="comment">#部署到Github   可缩写hexo d</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在浏览器中输入<a href="http://Github用户名.github.io">http://Github用户名.github.io</a> 就可以看到个人博客</p><p>也可以把部署命令写到deploy.sh里面，在命令行运行</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sh ./deploy.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
